"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Western democracy was born on the city-state civilization from Greece,if you look at the map you will see the geographic area is very segmented by ocean,most places are peninsula and mountain land\\nThat means it was very hard for a unified regime to control the whole part and also mountain land with less fertile land compared with the agricultural civilization neighbor（Accident Egypt,Babylonia) can not developed agriculture\\nThere are 2 notable features for Great Greece culture:\\n1,Freedom\\nNo unified regime means people of that part was relatively free and diversified ideologies and religions survived which developed the\\\"Freedom\\\" concept\\n2,Commercial Civilization\\nBecause of lacking good soil but nearby the agricultural countries,massive transactions made that logically consequenced the Commercial Civilization very early\\nThe commercial civilization shape the initial west society to cause the following points:\\n1,Spirit of contract\\nThis is the fundamental of transaction which can successfully carry on\\n2,Equality\\nIf you do business what you firstly care?\\nProfit! you don't care the gender,race,religion…etc.\\nThe goal is to make more profits,so that should emphasize \\\"everyone is equal\\\"\\n3,Innovation&adventure\\nBusiness man travels a lot,in the accident time they were natual adventurers,\\nand because lack of food which you need,people in Greece developed booming handcrafted industry,which request people always have new ideas to create the fancy stuff for which others were willing to pay…\",\"timestamp\":1633864288,\"title\":\"Reflection on western-democracy（part 1）\"},\"digest\":\"vASVxkjwC3PfQDffy7vtPoAXkXCvux0PK-X38ZCVR44\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x03197abAd8079143a69da8D037B6d69bcA469bcB\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"BYE6-bN2o1prUcjgaT7Y8fLeHwAEOPK6FJyZvAwQmxU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IVmQfWkuCP5WGiR1iQ